data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Cary, where the good vibes and the great outdoors collide! Tucked away on an oversized lot, this place isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade. With Bond Lake and Park practically in your backyard, you can access the trail right from your own turf—nature's not just knocking; it's part of the package!  And it's not just about the house; it's a community extravaganza. Clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, and even a pavilion for good measure. Those walking trails? They're more like your personal wonderland.  Step inside, and bam! Soaring ceilings making the place as bright as your future. Perfect for hosting epic gatherings. The 3-season room and deck are calling for chill hangouts. And the covered porch? It's a portal to the patio where memories are made.  But wait, there's a basement saga! Movie nights, zen moments, and a storage utopia—this basement has it all. Even a bedroom and full bath. And when you're feeling fancy, Downtown Cary and the new Cary Park are practically your neighbors. Less than 4 miles away, you can dive into the local buzz.  And here's the cherry on top—the roof's just 2 years old, the seller upgraded the light fixtures, doors, and hardware, and oh, there's a custom wood-burning fireplace with a floating mantle. It's not just a house; it's a masterpiece.  This home isn't just luxury; it's a lifestyle. Ready for the upgrade?
